{"tid":1250473,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【2019選票戰】最終戰術！7月2前血債票償","createTime":"2019-06-22T05:47:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-22T06:55:37.000Z","uid":267231,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"50909ada1e7db56781bc630c3564b4b8077f466b","tid":1250473,"uid":267231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T05:47:36.000Z","msg":"（請大家幫手forward，所有內容已向選舉事務處FACT CHECK!!!）<br />\n<br />\n第一步，我地嘗試以理服人。<br />\n第二步，我地改正確地址。<br />\n第三步，我地取消家中老人選民資格，免被利用！<br />\n<br />\n蛇齋餅糭要照拎，然後拎一張白紙寫封信去取消選民資格，7月2日前完成就可以取消今屆投票權！<br />\n<br />\n（信件格式）<br />\n<br />\n致選舉主任<br />\n<br />\n本人（全名）（身份證號碼）欲取消選民登記。登記地址為（地址），聯絡電話為（電話）。<br />\n<br />\n謝謝<br />\n（簽名）<br />\n<br />\n將文件郵寄至總選舉事務主任，選舉事務處，香港灣仔港灣道25號海港中心10樓、或傳真至(852) 2827 4644。<br />\n<br />\n緊記選舉事務處要在7月2日前收妥信件，才可取消本年度的投票權！<br />\n一封信件，保衛老友記，請即行動！"},{"pid":"3781a5aae1dc864578e4db355e261c08285f340f","tid":1250473,"uid":267231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T05:49:12.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"ee4f81cec46737f5ba7d76004899a3b04aaefff5","tid":1250473,"uid":267231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T05:50:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfc68c34b7298877f80faddb732a9f349c8f8d59","tid":1250473,"uid":267231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T05:51:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41e3a0545b4f5abe30a35958ff13ca89016ac576","tid":1250473,"uid":267231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T05:51:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8874d5e9daaaaae0ccc01d4df0c1fea69d9b9812","tid":1250473,"uid":18195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"scor